question: Within a radius of 70 kilometers, where can I find  a restaurant along the way to Chopper's Lawn Equipment, Kissimmee, FL from Lifestream Behavioral Center, Leesburg, FL?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.895483 28.836904)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.327543 28.262181)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.895483 28.836904)',4326)::geography, 70000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-81.895483 28.836904)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
